//!   1. `read_skill` is present in the registry's tool list.
//!   2. `{ name: "test-skill" }` returns the seeded body and lists sidecars.
//!   3. `{ name: "test-skill", file_path: "references/notes.md" }` returns
//!      the sidecar content.
